Titanic?

89
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,480
Is that true?

90
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:15,200
Did we lose to a 100-year-old man?

91
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:18,640
Since Mr. Liu retired from the shipyard,

92
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:21,800
