127
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:00,920
Chi Dayong.

128
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,240
[Dayong] Mm.

129
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:06,080
No.

130
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,040
