164
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,480
[grunts]

165
00:09:00,640 --> 00:09:03,280
[thwacking]

166
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:04,960
[pants]

167
00:09:09,840 --> 00:09:11,040
[thwacking]

168
