[grunting]

169
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:27,560
[whooshes]

170
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:33,880
[grunts]

171
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:35,920
[gasps]

172
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,440
[sighs deeply]

173
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:52,720
[exhales sharply]

174
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,680
I just changed the method.

175
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,320
Why is it not working?

176
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,320
[gasps]
A sudden change of method

177
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,800
doesn't really work.

178
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:04,320
At last, my opportunity of becoming
a main player has come.

179
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:08,920
[Lu Xia grunts]

180
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,680
[breathing heavily]

181
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,040
[groans]

182
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:23,760
[relieved sigh]

183
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:26,680
You use the snake-ball too often.

184
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:30,600
It drains your energy faster.

185
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,320
In certain circumstances,
you must be flexible.

186
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:37,360
I don't think so.
I should catch every single ball.

187
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:43,080
Stop being so stubborn,
or you will fall into their trap.

188
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:46,960
-Ahh.
-It is not only about winning.

189
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:49,360
-[sighs]
-You need wisdom and good judgment.

190
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:51,800
Give yourself more options.

191
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,840
A match is like a labyrinth

192
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,680
