and go the wrong way.

196
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:05,320
There is only one choice for me.

197
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,480
Hit the ball back.

198
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:10,720
If you have time,

199
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,800
go and help him.

200
