201
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:20,960
[gasps]

202
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:25,920
[panting]

203
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,600
[Lu Xia] I think I feel something.

204
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:31,760
YU QING

205
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:33,120
[Tang Jiale] Break us up?

206
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,960
I do not agree, Coach.

207
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:39,000
We only played badly today.

208
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:40,720
We have no other problems.

209
00:11:41,280 --> 00:11:43,560
Are you saying there really
isn't a problem,

210
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:45,200
or you just haven't realized it yet?

211
00:11:45,640 --> 00:11:47,640
[tense music]

212
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:53,600
I remember the first time you decided
to be partners.

213
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,600
It was the same as today.

214
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,920
You were standing here.

215
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:00,120
I told you then

216
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:03,680
