as the others can be.

220
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:13,200
So you have to trust
both your partner and yourself.

221
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,440
You work as a team.

222
00:12:15,040 --> 00:12:15,920
I...

223
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,920
[sighs]

224
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:21,360
Spotting a weakness is more difficult.

225
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:23,920
You know your partner too well.

226
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:27,000
Think about what you've done wrong.

227
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:28,680
Therefore,

228
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:32,320
I hope you could agree with me on this.

229
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,640
Make a decision.

230
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:36,440
Coach. Please...

231
00:12:36,840 --> 00:12:38,120
Please reconsider.

232
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:41,920
Chi Dayong.

233
00:12:43,280 --> 00:12:44,120
Coach.

234
00:12:45,760 --> 00:12:48,360
Jiale, stop it.

235
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,520
I agreed.

236
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,160
[gasps]

237
00:12:59,040 --> 00:13:01,040
[somber music]

238
00:13:04,760 --> 00:13:07,640
PROVINCIAL MATCH DI LIU HIGH SCHOOL
LIST OF COMPETITORS

239
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,960
Tang Jiale, Zhuo Zhi.

240
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:12,480
You knew beforehand?

241
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:15,120
Yan.

242
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:17,800
Did you arrange this?

243
00:13:19,760 --> 00:13:21,320
[Yan Zhiming] I just found out.

244
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,680
[sighs]
Don't look at me.

245
00:13:31,880 --> 00:13:33,120
It is the coach's decision.

246
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,680
The coach's decision?

247
00:13:34,880 --> 00:13:36,480
Why does she want to break you up?

248
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:42,880
[Siyang] For tomorrow's training,

249
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,800
