251
00:13:56,160 --> 00:13:57,120
Dachi.

252
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,880
Please get yourself prepared.

253
00:14:02,160 --> 00:14:03,000
Yes.

254
00:14:03,520 --> 00:14:04,480
Go.

255
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:10,960
[sighs]

256
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,680
Mind your step, stop playing.

257
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,520
I know what I am doing.

258
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:21,640
Eh?

259
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:23,560
[chuckles]

260
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,560
The finals is just around the corner.

261
00:14:27,800 --> 00:14:30,360
Why are you not training?
I can get the strings changed myself.

262
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:33,080
Because it's important
to accompany you as well.

263
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:35,160
[soft chuckle]

264
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:37,760
[light music]

265
00:14:49,480 --> 00:14:50,560
[Tang Jiale sighs]

266
00:14:56,120 --> 00:14:58,400
You look worried.

267
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:02,400
Okay, so the coach said
we should be separated.

268
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:03,720
But it's only temporary.

269
00:15:06,680 --> 00:15:07,600
Jiale,

270
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,720
even if we are not together,

271
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:11,640
