272
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,880
on my behalf.

273
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:15,520
[sighs]

274
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:17,920
We don't even understand
what the coach means

275
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,400
about us having a problem.

276
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,120
But I still believe

277
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,040
that we are the Golden Partners.

278
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,720
We will stay together forever.

279
00:15:30,080 --> 00:15:32,240
YU QING

280
